# Showing Saturns's position and aspect through time - Galen Gisler

clear
flag atmosphere off
flag landscape off
flag show_tui_datetime on

flag planet_names off
select planet Saturn
flag track_object on
wait duration 10
# first we look at Saturn's motion through the sky
timerate rate 30000000       # about ten months per second
wait duration 30

# then we look close up at Saturn's tilt changing with time
zoom fov 0.1 duration 10
wait duration 30
